  <brief_title>A New Reproducible Method of Measuring C/D Ratio of Digital Stereo Images of Optic Disc</brief_title>
  <official_title>A New Reproducible Method of Measuring C/D Ratio of Digital Stereo Images of Optic Disc</official_title>
